description: You’ve seen him on the Tonight Show with Jimmy Fallon, Adam Devine's House Party on Comedy Central, and Flophouse on Viceland. Now, hear him in your ears! He’s got a killer story set in his home state of Georgia. Here’s five words to describe this episode: be careful with hash pills.
